          'Our expertise is built on industry-leading best practices, ensuring your software is secure, efficient, and future-ready. By leveraging proven methodologies, we deliver solutions that meet the highest standards of quality and reliability',
        icon: 'tabler:list-check',
      },
      {
        title: 'Cost-effective strategies',
        description:
          'Maximize your ROI with our cost-effective strategies. We focus on delivering high-quality solutions that align with your budget, helping you achieve your goals without unnecessary expenses',
        icon: 'tabler:currency-pound',
